  <acceptance-criteria>
    <criterion testable="true">`SprkChatAgentFactory.CreateAgentAsync` queries `IWorkspaceStateService` per turn.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">"Workspace State" block appended to system prompt only when at least one tab has `visibleToAssistant: true`.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">Empty workspace produces no block (no whitespace pollution).</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">8K budget respected; truncation emits telemetry.</criterion>
    <criterion testable="true">No user message text from prior turns leaks into the workspace block (ADR-015).</criterion>
